</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify">此次IPO前，Andy Chang Liu持股为17.1%，顺为资本持股为20.2%，Fluency Holding持股为13.5%，H Capital持股为12.3%，CL Lion Investment III Limited持股为11.6%；</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Esta Investments Pte. Ltd.持股为11.2%，Walden Investments Group Limited持股为6.4%。Long Great Holdings Limited持股为5.8%。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201128/74dca041cb4648f8bec122ca1629541a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">IPO后，Andy Chang Liu持股15.5%，有81.7%的投票权；顺为资本持股为17%，有3.7%的投票权；H Capital持股为10.3%，有2.2%的投票权，CL Lion Investment III Limited持股为9.8%，有2.1%的投票权；</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Esta Investments Pte. Ltd.持股为9.4%，有2%的投票权；Walden Investments Group Limited持股为5.4%，有1.2%的投票权。Long Great Holdings Limited持股为4.9%，有1.1%的投票权。</p>
